Privacy Policy of
VerySport
Effective Date: January 15, 2025
Shenzhen DO Intelligent Technology Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as "VerySport" or "We") is committed to protecting your privacy in compliance with applicable laws on information protection and privacy. This privacy policy describes the information collected and processed by us when you use VerySport products and services. If you have any further questions on this privacy policy, please contact us via the email address at the end of this privacy policy.
