In addition, according to GDPR, you have the right to lodge a complaint with our supervisory authority.
12. Update of Privacy Policy
We will review our privacy policy on a regular basis and may update this privacy policy to reflect our changes to information practices. By using the product or service after our updated privacy policy is published, you will be deemed to accept the updated privacy policy. If you do not agree to any part of the privacy policy, you should immediately stop using our products and services.
